{
  "type": "sectionColumn",
  "id": "pipeline_section_c",
  "width": ["100%", "92%"],
  "contentWidth": ["100%", "min(92%, 80rem)"],
  "height": "hug",
  "marginTop": ["1.5rem", "3rem"],
  "marginBottom": ["1.5rem", "3rem"],
  "align": "center",
  "fill": "oklch(from var(--pb-secondary) l c h / 0.53)",
  "borderRadius": ["1.25rem", "2rem"],
  "effects": [{ "type": "backdropBlur", "amount": "20px" }],
  "columns": { "mobile": 1, "desktop": 2 },
  "columnWidths": { "mobile": [1], "desktop": [1.1, 1] },
  "columnGaps": { "mobile": "1rem", "desktop": "1.5rem" },
  "columnStyles": {
    "mobile": [{ "padding": "1rem", "gap": "1rem" }],
    "desktop": [
      { "padding": "1.5rem 1.75rem", "gap": "1rem", "alignY": "top" },
      { "padding": "1.5rem 1.75rem", "gap": "1rem", "alignY": "top" }
    ]
  },
  "itemStyles": {
    "mobile": {
      "pipeline-code": {
        "padding": "1rem",
        "fill": "var(--pb-secondary)",
        "borderRadius": "0.75rem"
      },
      "pipeline-diagram": {
        "padding": "1rem",
        "fill": "oklch(from var(--pb-on-secondary) l c h / 0.031)",
        "borderRadius": "0.75rem"
      }
    },
    "desktop": {
      "pipeline-code": {
        "padding": "1.25rem 1.5rem",
        "fill": "var(--pb-secondary)",
        "borderRadius": "0.75rem",
        "alignY": "top"
      },
      "pipeline-diagram": {
        "padding": "1.25rem 1.5rem",
        "fill": "oklch(from var(--pb-on-secondary) l c h / 0.031)",
        "borderRadius": "0.75rem",
        "alignY": "top"
      }
    }
  },
  "columnAssignments": {
    "mobile": { "pipeline-head": 0, "pipeline-code": 0, "pipeline-diagram": 0 },
    "desktop": { "pipeline-head": 0, "pipeline-code": 0, "pipeline-diagram": 1 }
  },
  "columnSpan": { "mobile": { "pipeline-head": "all" }, "desktop": { "pipeline-head": "all" } },
  "elementOrder": {
    "mobile": ["pipeline-head", "pipeline-code", "pipeline-diagram"],
    "desktop": ["pipeline-head", "pipeline-code", "pipeline-diagram"]
  },
  "definitions": {
    "pipeline-head": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "The pipeline in code",
      "width": "100%",
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": { "entrancePreset": "fade" }
    },
    "pipeline-code": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "The orchestrator—`getPage(slug)` runs the full pipeline and returns a resolved page or null:\n\n```ts\nexport async function getPage(slug: string): Promise<ResolvedPage | null> {\n  if (!isSafePathSegment(slug)) return null;\n  const page = loadPageBuilder(slug);\n  if (page == null || !isPageBuilder(page)) return null;\n  const assetBase = getAssetBaseUrl(page as ResolvedPage);\n  const { bg: expandedBg, sections: sectionsWithResolvedTriggers } = expandPageBuilder(page, { assetBase });\n  const sectionsWithInline3DAssets = await inlineModel3DAssets(sectionsWithResolvedTriggers);\n  return { ...page, bg: expandedBg, sections: sectionsWithInline3DAssets, definitions: page.definitions };\n}\n```",
      "level": 4,
      "width": "100%",
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideRight",
        "entranceMotion": { "transition": { "delay": 0.1 } }
      }
    },
    "pipeline-diagram": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "**Flow (ASCII):**\n\n```\nslug → LOAD (read page JSON, merge definitions, resolve presets)\n     → PageBuilder\n     → EXPAND (pure, sync: sectionOrder → sections, namespace columns, trigger refs, trigger payload URLs when assetBase provided)\n     → bg + sections\n     → RESOLVE (inlineModel3DAssets — only async)\n     → ResolvedPage\n     → RENDER (getPage → resolveSectionBlockUrls → PageBuilderRenderer)\n```",
      "level": 4,
      "width": "100%",
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideLeft",
        "entranceMotion": { "transition": { "delay": 0.15 } }
      }
    }
  }
}
